{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was connected with a formal examination during which it was theory as well as practical examination, which I did reasonably well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I became a toolmaker in March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now this is well into the progress of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What sort of information received?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you must understand one thing, that, you know, we are not living in a-- in a-- in a-- in a free-- in a free communication era, right?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The information we received was strictly censored [LAUGHS] and strictly directed and strictly under the, the final instruction of Goebbels, coming from as high up as that, right?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Look, gossip-- it was a very-- was a very difficult time for-- time, time for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in 1940, '41, up to '42 when the war started to turn in Stalingrad-- I remember from history that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler was extremely successful-- extremely successful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hitler got Austria, the Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had France in 1940, walked through-- around the Maginot Line in five minutes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got Holland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He got, got Belgium, Dunkirchen, Dunkirk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remember that?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Came-- Mhm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know what Dunkirchen is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The English--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dunkirk, yes, landed in, in Western Europe, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a malconceived landing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans beat the daylight out of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And poor fellows, they were standing in the-- in the water there, waiting for a ship to pick them up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they died by the thousands, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a humiliating defeat for the English at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, well, by the time, I, I, I very clearly saw where I belonged to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean-- I mean-- if-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] impressionable I was, but foolish I wasn't, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, I knew very clearly where I belonged to.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
